name: Rear Window 12x18 film poster
description:
Inspired by the wonderful film 'Rear Window', this listing is for a 12"x18" (ie 305 x 450 mm) print based on an original illustration by me, and printed by a professional print service on premium archival lustre paper.
This paper is water-resistant, fade-resistant, and has vibrant colours.
This print fits in a standard 12x18 inches frame and has no border. 

The print will be shipped in a protective tube, most likely recycled, within 3 working days of payment clearing.
___________________________________________________

INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING - IE OUTSIDE UK: PLEASE READ

Packages are sent by standard international post. This method is the most economic, but offers no tracking.

Shipping times outside the UK vary from 1 week to up to 4 weeks.
____________________________________________________

Thank you for looking
